summary: Lmao one of the highlights of Killing Eve 1x02 is how Konstantin “warns” Villanelle about a woman trying to find her and...
body:
Lmao one of the highlights of Killing Eve 1x02 is how Konstantin “warns” Villanelle about a woman trying to find her and goes “We’ll continue as usual. Just be aware” and Villanelle says “I’m always aware” in this very relaxed way but then she finds Eve’s picture on the internet and realizes it’s the same woman she met in the bathroom not long ago and you know on the inside she is just:

Because “always aware” my ass, Eve snuck into her life and she didn’t notice.

Eve: what’s missing? 
Villanelle, stammering: Th- the...
body:
Villanelle, bursts into the room: IT’S MISSING. OH MY GOD IT’S MISSING.

Eve: what’s missing?

Villanelle, stammering: Th- the thing!! I don’t know!!

Eve, turning around with their baby: what thing, babe?

Villanelle: Oh, nevermind you have it.

Eve: Wha-

Eve: YOU MEAN OUR DAUGHTER?!

blog.description:
I create BBC Sherlock podfic. Endless hours of our boys falling in love.

Buy Me a Coffee? (it only goes to offset costs of places to upload the podfic to)

Current WIP podfic status

The Grating Roar (by Engazed). Chapter 8 posted 6/23/19, new chapters will post each weekend.

Let Us Beware (by Prettyvk - WIP). Collection of short ficlets, companion pieces to The James Holmes Chronicles. I shall post updates as the author releases them.

And Your Very Flesh Shall Be A Great Poem (by CaitlinFairchild - WIP). The story has been dropped by the author unfinished, so I won't be able to finish the podfic. Sorry.

You come along because I love your face

Stop there and let me correct it, I want to live a life from a new perspective

You come along because I love your face

And I’ll admire your expensive taste

And who cares? Divine intervention

I want to be praised from a new perspective. But leaving now would be a good idea, so catch me up on getting out of here

Bonus: can we fast-forward til you go down on me?
